data.description: This ranch-style home is a great starter option or investment opportunity. The main level features three bedrooms, a full bathroom, a living area, and a functional kitchen. Step out onto the deck to enjoy the view of the yard overlooking a creek.  The lower level offers an additional bedroom, bathroom, and a family area. Updates are in progress, including a new stove, refrigerator, and water heater.  With some cosmetic updates, this home has great potential. It's a practical choice for those looking to make it their own or add it to their investment portfolio. Don't miss out on this chance to create your ideal living space.  Some photos are virtually staged.
